1021
01:58:57,714 --> 01:58:59,466
Superman's down there.

1022
01:59:00,467 --> 01:59:02,845
- You sure?
- Yeah.

1023
01:59:13,313 --> 01:59:15,941
- Richard!
- Yeah, I saw him. Strap in.

1024
01:59:44,678 --> 01:59:46,476
Lois!

1025
01:59:47,806 --> 01:59:49,604
Don't move.

1026
02:00:12,747 --> 02:00:13,873
[GASPS]

1027
02:00:35,687 --> 02:00:37,735
Come OH, come on, come on.

1028
02:00:39,107 --> 02:00:41,030
[ENGINE SPUTTERING]

1029
02:00:41,484 --> 02:00:43,202
Richard!

1030
02:00:43,361 --> 02:00:44,738
I'm trying! It's too choppy!

1031
02:00:53,872 --> 02:00:55,465
Oh, my God.

1032
02:01:18,521 --> 02:01:20,194
Ah.

1033
02:01:26,946 --> 02:01:28,289
[GRUNTING]

1034
02:01:31,242 --> 02:01:33,540
Ah!

1035
02:01:40,919 --> 02:01:43,013
Ah.

1036
02:01:46,466 --> 02:01:47,934
[LAUGHS]

1037
02:02:09,739 --> 02:02:11,207
Mom.

1038
02:02:12,158 --> 02:02:13,876
[SCREAMS]

1039
02:02:29,384 --> 02:02:30,977
Whoa.

1040
02:02:43,147 --> 02:02:45,149
How did you find me?

1041
02:02:50,655 --> 02:02:52,282
Thank you.

1042
02:03:07,255 --> 02:03:09,178
What are you doing?

1043
02:03:12,343 --> 02:03:13,595
I have to go back.

1044
02:03:16,306 --> 02:03:18,058
You're hurt!

1045
02:03:28,526 --> 02:03:30,199
Goodbye, Lois.

1046
02:04:24,540 --> 02:04:26,634
