1047
02:04:40,598 --> 02:04:43,078
<i>LEX [ON VIDEO]: Technology on Krypton,
Superman's home world...</i>

1048
02:04:43,102 --> 02:04:45,445
<i>was based on manipulating
the growth of crystals.</i>

1049
02:04:45,603 --> 02:04:46,980
<i>KITTY:
Sounds like Mom-Mom to me.</i>

1050
02:04:47,146 --> 02:04:50,992
<i>"LEX". Well, naturally, to the primitive mind,
any sufficiently advanced technology...</i>

1051
02:04:51,150 --> 02:04:53,118
<i>would be indistinguishable from magic.</i>

1052
02:04:53,277 --> 02:04:56,702
<i>But imagine: Cities, vehicles, weapons...</i>

1053
02:04:56,864 --> 02:04:59,367
<i>entire continents, all grown.</i>

1054
02:04:59,534 --> 02:05:01,286
- KITTY: Lex?
- Uh-huh.

1055
02:05:03,121 --> 02:05:06,250
Are billions of people really going to die?

1056
02:05:12,755 --> 02:05:14,473
Yes.

1057
02:05:21,222 --> 02:05:23,316
[RUMBLING]

1058
02:05:41,826 --> 02:05:43,169
Lex, what's happening?

1059
02:05:49,125 --> 02:05:50,752
Go, go, go. Get to the helicopter.

1060
02:05:53,629 --> 02:05:56,007
Go! Out, out! Now!

1061
02:05:59,177 --> 02:06:02,351
No, no, no, take nothing!
Take nothing! Go, go!

1062
02:06:04,265 --> 02:06:05,858
Got it.

1063
02:06:39,926 --> 02:06:41,519
[WHIMPERS]

1064
02:06:49,977 --> 02:06:51,570
Here.

1065
02:07:15,461 --> 02:07:17,429
- What did you do?
- I'm sorry!

1066
02:07:17,588 --> 02:07:19,181
No!

1067
02:07:36,607 --> 02:07:38,200
[CRYING]

1068
02:07:38,734 --> 02:07:42,329
- What did you do?
- I'm sorry!

1069
02:07:47,952 --> 02:07:49,875
[RUMBLING]

