No hemorrhage.

1080
02:12:29,316 --> 02:12:30,659
Shock at 200.

1081
02:12:30,818 --> 02:12:32,661
WOMAN 5:
Ls that enough? He's not human.

1082
02:12:32,820 --> 02:12:34,493
MAN 6:
All right, charge to three, 360.

1083
02:12:34,655 --> 02:12:36,248
Clear!

1084
02:12:50,045 --> 02:12:52,468
[EKG Mom]

1085
02:13:06,896 --> 02:13:08,296
RICHARD:
It's kind of morbid, Perry.

1086
02:13:09,023 --> 02:13:11,492
Always be prepared.

1087
02:13:13,861 --> 02:13:15,579
How is she?

1088
02:13:30,294 --> 02:13:31,796
Oh.

1089
02:13:35,090 --> 02:13:38,094
Thank you. Thanks, baby.

1090
02:13:40,888 --> 02:13:42,105
- Lois?
- Yeah.

1091
02:13:44,308 --> 02:13:46,231
We can leave whenever you're ready.

1092
02:13:46,393 --> 02:13:47,940
I mean...

1093
02:13:49,563 --> 02:13:51,565
you don't have to be here.

1094
02:13:52,775 --> 02:13:54,618
Where else would I be?

1095
02:13:54,777 --> 02:13:56,620
<i>MAN [ON TV]:
Police have surrounded the area...</i>

1096
02:13:56,820 --> 02:13:58,413
<i>to control thousands of visitors...</i>

1097
02:13:58,572 --> 02:14:00,415
<i>who have arrived
to show their support.</i>

1098
02:14:00,574 --> 02:14:02,372
<i>Many are carrying signs and banners...</i>

1099
02:14:02,535 --> 02:14:03,957
I could drive.

1100
02:14:04,119 --> 02:14:06,588
<i>No official announcements
over the past few hours...</i>

1101
02:14:06,747 --> 02:14:09,296
<i>but unconfirmed reports
from inside tell us...</i>

1102
02:14:09,458 --> 02:14:11,301
<i>the Man of Steel lies in a coma...</i>

1103
02:14:11,460 --> 02:14:15,966
<i>his condition unchanged
since he was admitted late yesterday.</i>

1104
02:14:21,095 --> 02:14:22,972
<i>"WOMAN".
Doctors have been vigilant in their...</i>

1105
02:14:23,138 --> 02:14:24,435
<i>MAN".
Foreign exchange markets...</i>

1106
02:14:24,890 --> 02:14:27,939
- Where are you going?
