1125
02:17:57,686 --> 02:17:59,984
[LOIS WHISPERING]

1126
02:18:18,665 --> 02:18:21,509
[HEART MONITOR BEEPING]

1127
02:18:38,352 --> 02:18:40,229
Come on, honey.

1128
02:19:02,000 --> 02:19:04,094
[CROWD CHATTERING]

1129
02:19:23,939 --> 02:19:26,067
MAN: Step back, please!

1130
02:19:41,790 --> 02:19:43,087
[YELLS]

1131
02:19:43,250 --> 02:19:46,971
Lex, we only have six of those!

1132
02:19:48,881 --> 02:19:50,178
Six?

1133
02:19:50,799 --> 02:19:53,598
[LAUGHS MANIACALLY]

1134
02:19:53,969 --> 02:19:58,315
I would trade 300,000 coconuts...

1135
02:19:58,473 --> 02:20:00,817
and every ounce of your blood...

1136
02:20:00,976 --> 02:20:05,607
for a quart of gasoline!

1137
02:20:06,315 --> 02:20:08,989
KITTY:
But what will we have to eat?

1138
02:20:44,811 --> 02:20:46,609
[ALARM BEEPING]

1139
02:22:45,140 --> 02:22:47,234
You will be different.

1140
02:22:50,896 --> 02:22:53,866
Sometimes, you will feel like an outcast.

1141
02:22:54,983 --> 02:22:57,736
But you'll never be alone.

1142
02:23:00,113 --> 02:23:02,787
You will make my strength your own.

1143
02:23:05,744 --> 02:23:09,465
You will see my life through your eyes...

1144
02:23:10,332 --> 02:23:15,680
as your life will be seen through mine.

1145
02:23:27,307 --> 02:23:31,357
The son becomes the father...

1146
02:23:33,021 --> 02:23:37,822
and the father becomes the son.

1147
02:24:17,232 --> 02:24:18,654
